  <h1>Responsible Gambling Tactics</h1>
  <p>The purpose of this website is to provide gamblers with rules, guidleines, and calculators to avoid betting
    mistakes and placing bad bets.</p>
  <p>Don't be the one to squanders your childs college fund!</p>
  <img src=https://bestbingouk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Gambling-Problems-2048x1366.jpg alt="Gambling" width="350"
    height="200"">
    <h3>Rules</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Do not bet more than algorithm states.</li>
      <li>Never gamble under any influences.</li>
      <li>Do not chase.</li>
    </ol>
    <h3>General rules</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Only bet up to 10% of your bankroll on a bet.</li>
      <li>Avoid parlays.</li>
      <li>Hunt for value in bets.</li>
      <li>Learn to find an edge.</li>
    </ul>

    <a href=" glossay.html">Glossary</a>

